                            <comment id="14598605" author="benedict" created="Tue, 23 Jun 2015 23:57:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Filed &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9642&quot; title=&quot;getSplits should not depend on selectAndReference()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-9642&quot;&gt;CASSANDRA-9642&lt;/a&gt; as a follow up, to ensure the &lt;tt&gt;getSplits&lt;/tt&gt; method behaves well in the face of any future problems here (although in 2.2 this particular bug is already mitigated, and the risk is generally reduced from 2.2 onwards, there&apos;s no reason not to further ensure its good behaviour)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
